    @MappedSuperclass
public abstract class WebCmsObjectSuperClass<T extends WebCmsObjectSuperClass<T>>
extends com.foreach.across.modules.hibernate.business.SettableIdAuditableEntity<T>
implements WebCmsObject, WebCmsDomainBound
    Base implementation for a WebCmsObject entity that ensures that the object id is part of an object collection. Requires the entity table to have a object_id column with a max length of 100.

    This is a base class for single entities, if you want a base class for an inheritance strategy, consider using the WebCmsObjectInheritanceSuperClass.

    Since:
    0.0.1
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
    See Also:
    WebCmsObjectInheritanceSuperClass
